{
  "texts": [
    "It has since been available to the general public for research.",
    "Figure 1 shows samples of the adopted TrashNet dataset.",
    "The adopted dataset's class distribution suffers from a class imbalance problem as can be observed from Fig. 2.",
    "The trash class is a minority class since it has a lot fewer samples than the other classes.",
    "Class imbalance can have a negative influence on machine learning model performance since the model may be biased toward the majority class."
  ]
}